pack-for-cpan       2010-07-15 09:39:51

How to pack up this module for release via CPAN, step-by-step

1.  Download Smart::Comments from CPAN: 

        http://search.cpan.org/CPAN/authors/id/C/CH/CHORNY/Smart-Comments-1.0.4.tar.gz
        
        $ mkdir ~/projects/smartlog/pack
        $ cd pack
        
        Extract the tarball into pack/.
        
2.  Create a skeleton using module-starter: 
        
        $ module-starter --module=Smart::Comments::Any
        $ mv Smart-Comments-Any Smart-Comments-Any-1.1.0
        
3.  
